Fiye da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli jawabin da aka yi a ranar Alhamis na mai neman kujerar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh da matar da ta zarge shi da aikata laifukan jima'i da ake zargin sun faru ne a shekarun 1980s, Christine Blasey Ford, a tashoshin talabijin shida.
A halin yanzu, hargitsi na siyasa ya ci gaba, inda masu watsa shirye-shirye suka katse shirin na yau da kullum don bayar da rahoton abin da ba a zata ba a ranar Juma'a: yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya tsara don FBI ta gudanar da bincike na mako guda kan zargin.
Ford ya shaida wa kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa cewa matar ta tabbata cewa Kavanaugh ya yi masa ba'a a lokacin da ya bugu kuma ya yi kokarin cire tufafinsa a lokacin bikin makarantar sakandare.
Kavanaugh, a cikin shaidar sa mai zafi, ya ce yana da tabbacin cewa hakan bai faru ba.
Wataƙila sama da mutane miliyan 20.4 da Nielsen ta ruwaito a ranar Juma'a, sun kalli bidiyon.
Kamfanin ya lissafa matsakaicin masu kallo a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a samun lissafi na wasu tashoshin da ke watsa wannan a hanzari, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Kuma Nielsen yawanci yana da matsala wajen kirga yawan mutanen da suke kallon sa a ofishinsa.
Don a saka wannan a cikin mahangar, wannan shine yawan masu kallo kusan kamar wasan ƙwallon ƙafa ko kuma kyautar Academy.
