Shugaban Mexico, AMLO, ya yi alkawarin ba zai yi amfani da sojoji ba wajen yaki da fararen hula
Shugaban kasa Andres Manuel Lopez Obrador ya sha alwashin cewa ba zai taba amfani da karfin soja ba akan fararen hula a gaban bikin cika shekaru 50 da kisan gilla da aka yi wa dalibai.
