LeBron zai fara buga wasan Lakers a ranar Lahadi a San Diego
Fans suna jiran ganin LeBron James ya fara wasa a Los Angeles Lakers.
Kocin Lakers Luke Walton ya sanar da cewa James zai buga wasan farko na kakar wasa ta farko a ranar Lahadi da Denver Nuggets a San Diego.
Duk da haka, ba a bayyana tsawon lokacin da zai yi wasa ba.
"Za a yi fiye da ɗaya kuma ƙasa da 48", in ji Walton a shafin yanar gizon Lakers.
Dan jaridar Lakers Mike Trudell ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa James zai buga wasan ne cikin 'yan mintoci kaɗan.
Bayan atisayen farko na wannan makon, an tambayi James game da shirinsa na shirya wasanni shida na kakar wasa ta Lakers.
"A halin da nake ciki a sana'ata, ba na bukatar yin wasannin kakar wasa don in shirya", in ji shi.
Taron Trump na yammacin Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara taron neman zabensa da yammacin yau a birnin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne taron farko na Trump na taro biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da tsayawa a wurare masu ban sha'awa da suka hada da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Bayan tabbatar da cewa an jinkirta zaben domin ya zabi wanda zai rike kujerar kotun koli, Trump ya yi niyyar gina goyon baya a gare shi a zaben da za a yi a lokacin da jam'iyyar Republican ke fuskantar asarar iko a majalisa idan aka yi zaben a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a West Virginia za a yi kuma ta yaya za ka iya kallonsa a kan layi?
An shirya taron Trump na gari a Wheeling, West Virginia da karfe 7 na dare, wannan daren, Asabar, 29 ga watan Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia ta hanyar YouTube.
Trump zai yi jawabi a wannan makon game da zaben Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ke fuskantar tashin hankali bayan zargin cin zarafin mata da kuma cewa za a dage zaben majalisar dattawa har mako guda, yayin da FBI ke bincike a kan lamarin.
Amma babban abin da ake so a yi shi ne taimaka wa jam'iyyar Republican ta samu ci gaba a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Saboda haka, an bayyana a cikin yakin neman zaben Shugaba Trump cewa taron jama'a guda biyar a mako mai zuwa na nufin "bokan masu ba da agaji da masu goyon baya yayin da jam'iyyar Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjaye da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai", a cewar Reuters.
"Sarrafa majalisa yana da matukar muhimmanci ga ajandarsa saboda haka shugaban zai yi tafiye-tafiye zuwa jihohi da dama yayin da muke fuskantar lokacin kamfen mai cike da aiki", in ji mai magana da yawun yakin neman zaben Trump wanda ya nemi a sakaya sunansa ya shaida wa Reuters.
An shirya taron a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, ana sa ran taron zai samu masu goyon baya daga "Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma janyo hankalin kafofin watsa labarai daga Pittsburgh", in ji West Virginia Metro News.
Ranar Asabar za ta zama ziyarar Trump ta biyu a West Virginia a cikin wata guda, jihar da ya lashe zaben da ya wuce kashi 40 cikin dari a 2016.
Trump ya yi kokarin taimaka wa Patrick Morrisey, dan takarar Sanata na Jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia wanda ya fadi a baya a kuri'un.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ga Morrisey cewa shugaban zai zo ne a kokarin da zai kara yawan amsoshinsa a zaben", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
Ryder Cup 2018: Ƙungiyar Amurka ta nuna ƙarfin hali ta riƙe begenta a wasan ƙwallon ƙafa na ranar Lahadi
Bayan an yi zaman guda uku, an yi zaman hudu a ranar Asabar da yamma, wanda zai zama dole a gasar Ryder.
Motsawa da motsi shine ra'ayin wasanni wanda shine sakamakon binciken da 'yan wasa suka yarda da shi, kuma babu wanda ya wuce wannan a irin wannan gasa.
Ina suke ganin lokacin da muke ciki?
"A baya, sun yi nasara da maki shida kuma yanzu sun yi nasara da maki hudu, don haka ina ganin muna ganin hakan a matsayin wani abu ne mai karfafa gwiwa", in ji Jordan Spieth yayin da yake wucewa ranar.
Babu shakka Turai tana da fa'ida domin tana da maki huɗu a gaba da wasanni goma sha biyu.
Amma Team America, kamar yadda Spieth ya ce, suna jin suna da ɗan ƙarfi kuma suna da abubuwa da yawa da za su iya zama masu ƙarfi, ban da tsarin Spieth da Justin Thomas waɗanda ke wasa tare a duk rana kuma kowannensu yana alfahari da maki uku daga cikin huɗu.
Spieth ya yi wasa da kyau daga tee har zuwa green kuma ya jagoranci da kyau.
Muryar murna da take yi ta kara ƙaruwa yayin da ta kai ga lokacinta, ta yi muhimmin bugun da ya sa aka ci wasan a matsayin wasan da ta yi da Thomas biyu biyu.
Wasan da ya buga wanda ya lashe su a lamba 15 an yi masa maraba da irin wannan ihu, ihu da ke gaya maka cewa ya tabbata Amurka ba ta rasa ba.
"Ya kamata ka yi ƙoƙari sosai kuma ka damu da wasan da kanka", in ji Spieth.
Dukan waɗannan 'yan wasan sun tafi yanzu.
Akwai ramuka 18 da za a yi wa alama.
'Yan wasa guda daya da suka ci Spieth da Thomas a cikin kwanaki biyu da suka gabata sune Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, labarin da ba a iya musantawa ba daga gasar Ryder.
Ƙungiya mai ban sha'awa amma mai ban sha'awa daga Turai shine hudu zuwa hudu kuma zai iya yin ba tare da kuskure ba.
"Moliwood" ita ce kawai ma'aurata da ba su yi bogey a ranar Asabar da yamma ba, amma sun kuma guje wa bogey a ranar Asabar da safe, Jumma'a da yamma da kuma baya tara a ranar Jumma'a da safe.
Wannan gudu, da kuma yadda suke ganin suna da kuzari suna gudana zuwa da kuma daga cikin wannan taron jama'a sun tabbatar da cewa su ne 'yan wasan da za a doke su a ranar Lahadi, kuma babu wani dan wasa da ya fi Fleetwood da Molinari shahara wanda zai kulle damar cin nasarar Turai a lokacin da rana ta faɗi a kan Le Golf National.
Zai fi kyau idan a lokaci guda an sanya su a cikin rami daban-daban.
Amma, har yanzu bai yi nisa ba kafin a yi magana game da nasara a Turai.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun rage aikin Sergio Garcia, gwarzon wasan kwallon kafa na safe, lokacin da aka haɗa shi da Alex Noren.
Wani bogey da biyu a gaban tara kamar yadda ake haƙa rami wanda waɗannan 'yan wasan golf na Spain da Sweden ba za su taɓa hawa ba.
Ko da yake, a ranar Lahadi babu wanda zai iya taimaka maka fita daga cikin rami.
Kwallon hudu da na hudu suna da kyau sosai don a duba su a hankali saboda hulɗar da ke tsakanin ma'aurata, shawarwarin da suke bayarwa, shawarwarin da ba su bayar ba da kuma yadda dabarun zasu iya canzawa a cikin lokaci.
Ya zuwa yanzu, Turai ta fi kyau a matsayin ta kuma ta yi gaba sosai zuwa ranar karshe, amma zaman na hudu ya nuna cewa tawagar Amurka tana da ƙarfin gwiwa don yin wasa duk da shakku daga wasu, musamman a Amurka.
Turai ta yi nasara 10-6 a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup
Turai za ta yi amfani da damar da take da ita a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup bayan ta tashi daga wasan kwallon hudu da na hudu a ranar Asabar da ta yi nasara da 10-6 a kan Amurka.
Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci biyu da Tiger Woods wanda ya yi gwagwarmaya don samun maki a Le Golf National da maki hudu.
Ƙungiyar Turai Thomas Bjorn, wadda ke neman kare kofin da ta rasa a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ta mamaye tawagar Amurka da ta yi kuskure a wasan kwallon kafa na safe, ta sa wasan ya zama 3-1.
Amurka ta ba da ƙarin juriya a cikin foursome, ta ci wasanni biyu, amma ba za su iya rage rashi ba.
Kungiyar Jim Furyk na bukatar maki takwas daga wasanni 12 na wasa a ranar Lahadi domin kare kofin.
Fleetwood shine farkon dan wasan Turai na farko da ya ci maki hudu a jere, yayin da shi da Molinari, wanda aka yi wa lakabi da "Molliwood" bayan karshen mako mai ban mamaki, sun zama kawai na biyu da suka ci maki hudu daga cikin wasanninsu huɗu a tarihin Ryder Cup.
Bayan sun doke Woods da Patrick Reed a wasan kwallon kafa, sun yi nasara sosai a kan Woods da dan wasan Amurka Bryson Dechambeau da ci 5 da 4.
Woods, wanda ya yi ta fama da wasanni biyu a ranar Asabar, ya yi fice a wasu lokutan amma ya riga ya rasa wasanni 19 daga cikin 29 a wasan kwallon hudu da na hudu da kuma bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, ya huta a wasan kwallon kafa na safe, sai ya koma ya yi wasa da Henrik Stenson a wasan hudu kuma ya ci 2&1 daga Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka - wadanda suka kasance na daya da na uku a duniya.
Turai ba ta kai ta ba duk da cewa rana tana da kyau kuma iska tana iska a kudu maso yammacin Paris.
Manyan masu cin kofin sau uku Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas sun kafa wa Amurkawa kwallo da maki biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun sami nasara 2&1 mai ban sha'awa akan Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter na Spain a cikin hudu sannan suka dawo don doke Poulter da Rory McIlroy 4&3 a cikin hudu bayan sun rasa ramuka biyu na farko.
Sau biyu ne kawai a tarihin Ryder Cup inda wata kungiya ta dawo daga ragamar maki hudu ta shiga wasan daya, duk da cewa a matsayin mai tsaron ragamar kungiya Furyk tana bukatar maki ne kawai don kare kofin.
Amma, bayan sun yi kwanaki biyu suna samun nasara, sai dai a ranar Lahadi, sun yi ta neman nasara.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce ba zai yiwu ba a yi watsi da makaman da aka yi ba tare da amincewa ba
A ranar Asabar, Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya sanar da Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa takunkumin na kara tsananta musu kan Amurka kuma ba zai yiwu kasar ta kwashe makaman nukiliyarta ba a cikin irin wannan yanayi.
Ri Yong Ho ya shaida wa babban taron kungiyar shekara-shekara cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki "matakai masu muhimmanci da ke nuna kyakkyawar niyya" a shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da makamai masu linzami, rushe wuraren gwajin nukiliya, da kuma alkawarin ba za ta ci gaba da bunkasa makaman nukiliya da fasahar nukiliya ba.
"Duk da haka, ba mu ga wani martani na dacewa daga Amurka ba", in ji shi.
"Ba tare da amincewa da Amurka ba za a sami amincewa da tsaron kasa ba kuma a irin wannan yanayi ba zai yiwu mu cire makamanmu ba da farko".
Yayin da Ri ya maimaita irin wannan korafin na Koriya ta Arewa game da juriyar Washington ga "matakai" na hana nukiliya wanda za a hukunta Koriya ta Arewa saboda daukar matakai na mataki-mataki, muhimmin sanarwa da ya bayar shi ne cewa ba su yi watsi da shi gaba daya ba kamar yadda Pyongyang ta yi a baya.
Ri ya yi nuni ne ga wata sanarwa da Kim Jong Un da Donald Trump suka yi a taron koli tsakanin jami'an shugaban Amurka da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa da aka fara gudanarwa a Singapore a ranar 12 ga watan Yuni, a lokacin da Kim ya yi alkawarin yin kokarin "rashin makaman nukiliya na yankin Koriya" yayin da Trump ya yi alkawarin tabbatar da tsaron Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa ta nemi a kawo karshen yakin Koriya na 1950-53 a hukumance, amma Amurka ta ce dole ne Pyongyang ta dakatar da makaman nukiliya da farko.
Har ila yau, Washington ta yi watsi da kira ga sassauta takunkumin kasa da kasa kan Koriya ta Arewa.
"Amurka ta dage kan "kawar da makaman nukiliya da farko" kuma ta kara matsin lamba ta hanyar takunkumin da ke da makamancin cimma burinta ta hanyar tilasta, har ma ta ki amincewa da "sanarwar karshen yaki"," in ji Ri.
"Hankalin cewa takunkumi zai sa mu durƙusa a kan gwiwoyinmu ruɗu ne na mutanen da ba su san mu ba.
Amma matsalar ita ce, irin wannan takunkumi zai sa mu ƙara rashin amincewa da juna".
Ri bai ambaci shirin taron koli na biyu tsakanin Kim da Trump ba wanda shugaban Amurka ya yi sharhi a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon wannan makon.
Maimakon haka, ministan ya yi nuni da ganawa uku da Kim ya yi da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Moon Jae-in a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata, ya daɗa cewa: "Idan Koriya ta Kudu ce ke da matsala a wannan batun na kawar da makaman nukiliya maimakon Amurka, ba za a sami irin wannan hanyar ba".
Duk da haka, sautin jawabin Ri ya bambanta da na shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da ya yi magana a gaban Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa harbin makaman nukiliya na Koriya ta Arewa a kan Amurka ba makawa ne bayan "Shugaban Iblis" Trump ya kira Kim "mutumin roka" a kan aikin kashe kansa.
A wannan shekara a taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Trump wanda a bara ya yi barazanar "hallaka" Koriya ta Arewa gaba daya, ya yaba wa Kim saboda karfin gwiwar da ya nuna wajen daukar matakin cirewa, amma har yanzu akwai babban aiki da za a yi kuma dole ne a ci gaba da sanya takunkumi har sai Koriya ta Arewa ta yi watsi da makaman nukiliya.
A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce ba shi da wani lokaci na wannan, "idan ya dauki shekaru biyu, shekaru uku ko watanni biyar - babu matsala", in ji shi.
Sin da Rasha sun ce ya kamata kwamitin sulhu na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya hukunta Pyongyang saboda matakin da ta dauka.
Sai dai kuma, Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo, ya sanar da Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta Tsaro a ranar Alhamis cewa: "Ya kamata a ci gaba da aiwatar da takunkumin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya da karfi kuma kada a kasa har sai mun san cewa haramcin makaman nukiliya na karshe ne, kuma an tabbatar da shi".
Kwamitin Tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya amince da kara takunkumin da ya kafa kan Koriya ta Arewa tun a shekarar 2006 a kokarin da ake yi na dakatar da shirin nukiliya da makamai masu linzami na Pyongyang.
Pompeo ya gana da Ri a gefen babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya kuma ya ce bayan hakan zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe don shirya taron koli na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekara, amma tafiyarsa ta karshe ba ta yi kyau ba.
Ya bar Pyongyang a watan Yuli yana mai cewa a zahiri an samu ci gaba, sai dai Koriya ta Arewa a cikin sa'o'i kadan ta ce tana yin "bugun zargi kamar 'yan bindiga".
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin a wani taro da Moon ya yi a wannan watan cewa za ta cire makaman nukiliya da kuma wuraren da ake da makaman nukiliya idan Amurka ta dauki matakin da ya dace.
Ya bayyana cewa Kim ya umarce shi da ya yi "aiki" da ya dace da burinsa na tabbatar da tsaro da Trump ya yi alkawari a Singapore da kuma ci gaba da daidaita dangantakar da ke tsakanin kasar da Washington.
Daliban Harvard sun ɗauki darasi game da samun isashen hutu
Wani sabon darasi a Harvard a wannan shekara ya sa dukan ɗaliban S1 a can suka sami ƙarin barci, a ƙoƙarin da suke yi na yaƙi da al'adun macho na koyo da ke tasowa ta hanyar 'yan adam na owl' da ke da iko da maganin kafeyin.
Wani masanin kimiyya ya gano cewa ɗalibai a manyan jami'o'i a duniya sau da yawa ba su san kome ba game da ainihin yadda za su kāre kansu.
Charles Czeisler, farfesa a fannin barci a Makarantar Kiwon Lafiya ta Harvard da kuma gwani a asibitin Brigham da Women's, ya tsara wannan darasi, wanda ya gaskata shi ne na farko a ƙasar Amirka.
Ta samu kwarin gwiwa ta fara wannan darasi ne bayan ta gabatar da wani darasi game da tasirin rashin barci a kan ilmantarwa.
'A ƙarshe wata yarinya ta zo wurina ta ce: 'Me ya sa aka gaya mini yanzu, a shekaruna na ƙarshe?'
Yarinyar ta ce babu wanda ya taɓa gaya mata game da muhimmancin barci - abin da ya ba ni mamaki,' in ji ta ga The Telegraph.
Darasi da aka fara gabatar da shi a wannan shekara, ya bayyana wa ɗalibai muhimmancin yadda kyawawan halaye na barci ke taimakawa ga nasarorin ilimi da na wasanni, da kuma inganta lafiyarsu gaba ɗaya.
Paul Barreira, farfesa a fannin ilimin halayyar ɗan adam a Makarantar Kiwon Lafiya ta Harvard kuma shugaban ayyukan kula da lafiyar jami'ar, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da wannan darasi ne bayan ta ga cewa ɗalibai suna rashin barci sosai a mako.
Wannan darasi na awa ɗaya yana ɗauke da ayyuka masu ma'ana.
A wani zaman, an nuna hotunan dakunan kwanan dalibai, inda ɗalibai suke danna kofi, labule, wando, da littattafai don su fahimci tasirin maganin kafeyin da hasken wuta, da kuma yadda rashin barci ke shafar wasan motsa jiki, da kuma muhimmancin yin barci a kai a kai.
A wani sashe kuma, an bayyana wa masu halarta yadda rashin barci zai iya ƙara haɗarin kamuwa da ciwon zuciya, bugun jini, baƙin ciki, da kuma ciwon daji.
Taswirar harabar makarantar, tare da gumaka masu ma'ana, sannan ta sa masu halarta su yi tunani game da al'adunsu na yau da kullum.
'Mun san cewa wannan ba zai canja halayen ɗalibai nan take ba.
Amma mun tabbata cewa suna da hakkin su sani - kamar yadda kuke da hakkin ku san tasirin shan taba a kan lafiyarku,' in ji Farfesa Czeisler.
Ya ce, al'adun 'girma' suna nan, sai kuma fasahar zamani da kuma matsin lamba ga ɗalibai wanda ke nufin rashin barci matsala ce mai girma.
Ya ce, samun isashen barci mai kyau ya kamata ya zama 'makamin sirri' don magance damuwa, gajiya, da kuma damuwa - har ma don guje wa samun ƙarin nauyi, domin rashin barci yana sa kwakwalwa ta fara jin yunwa, yana sa mutum ya ci gaba da jin yunwa.
Raymond So, wani ɗan California mai shekara 19 da yake nazarin ilimin sunadarai da kuma ilimin lissafi wanda ya taimaki Farfesa Czeisler ya tsara wannan darasin, ya ɗauki ɗaya daga cikin darussansa a shekarar da ta shige a shekara ta farko a Harvard.
Ya ce wannan darasi ya buɗe masa ido kuma ya sa ya shirya darasi a dukan makarantar.
Mataki na gaba, yana fatan cewa duk daliban digiri na biyu za a koya musu su kammala irin wannan tsarin karatun kafin su shiga wata cibiyar gasa.
Farfesa Czeisler ya ba da shawarar cewa ɗalibai su yi la'akari da kafa ƙararrawa na barci, da kuma ƙararrawa na farkawa, kuma su fahimci tasirin haske mai shuɗi da ke fitowa daga allon lantarki da fitilun LED, wanda zai iya sauya saurin circadian ɗinku daga layin da ke haifar da matsalar bacci.
Livingston 1-0 Rangers: kwallo ya rage tunanin sojojin Gerrard
Har ila yau, Rangers sun ji bakin ciki a ranar da Dolly ta kai hari a kan tawagar Steven Gerrard da aka saki a cikin rashin nasara 1-0 a Livingston.
Kungiyar Ibrox na kokarin samun nasarar farko a kan hanyarsu, tun bayan nasarar 4-1 da suka samu a watan Fabrairu a St Johnstone, amma kungiyar Gary Holt ta kawo karshen kayar da Gerrard a wasanni 18 a matsayin kocin, inda ya sa ta sauka da maki takwas a gaban jagoran Ladbrokes Premiership Hearts.
Ya kai hari da minti bakwai kafin wasan farko ya kare kuma 'yan wasan Rangers sun yi kasa-kasa da alama ba za su iya daidaitawa ba.
Yayin da Rangers suka koma matsayi na shida, Livingston ya hau matsayi na uku, yana da nisa da Hibernian.
Kuma za a iya samun karin matsala a sansanin Rangers bayan da aka yi wa Calum Spence da ke tsaron layin layin magani sakamakon raunin da ya samu a kai bayan da aka jefa masa wani abu daga nesa.
Gerrard ya yi sau takwas a tawagar da ta tsallake Ayr zuwa wasan kusa da na karshe na gasar cin kofin Betfred.
A maimakon haka, Holt ya tafi da Livi 11 wanda ya ci Hearts a makon da ya gabata kuma zai yi farin ciki da tufafin da zai burge abokan hamayyarsu a kowane lokaci.
Rangers sun fi kowa mallakar ƙwallon, amma Livingston ya fi amfani da ƙwallon da suke da shi.
Ya kamata su ci kwallo cikin minti biyu lokacin da Scott Pittman ya jefa wa dan wasan kwallo a raga, amma dan wasan ya yi amfani da damar da ya samu.
Keaghan Jacobs ya yi nasara a wasan da ya kai ga kyaftin din Craig Halkett amma abokin wasansa Alan Lithgow ya yi nasara a wasan da ya kai ga buga ƙwallo a baya.
Rangers sun dauki iko amma da alama akwai fatan da yawa fiye da tabbaci game da wasansu a wasan karshe na uku.
Alfredo Morelos ya ji cewa ya kamata a yi masa horo lokacin da shi da Steven Lawless suka yi karo a alamar karfe goma amma mai wasan kwaikwayo Steven Thomson ya ki amincewa da wannan roƙon ɗan Colombia.
Rangers sun yi nasara ne kawai a wasan farko amma mai tsaron gidan Ibrox, Liam Kelly, bai taba samun matsala ba tare da Lassana Coulibaly da Ovie Ejaria.
Ko da yake kwallo na farko da Livi ya ci a minti na 34 ya saɓa wa yadda wasan ya kasance, babu wanda zai ce sun cancanci hakan saboda aikin da suka yi.
Har ila yau, Rangers sun kasa cin nasara a kan dabarun Jacobs na zurfin matattu.
Scott Arfield bai amsa ba lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya sanya kwallon zuwa Scott Robinson, wanda ya kasance mai nutsuwa ya zaɓi Menga don ƙarshen sauƙi.
Gerrard ya yi aiki a lokacin hutu ta hanyar maye gurbin Coulibaly da Ryan Kent kuma ya yi tasiri kai tsaye lokacin da dan wasan ya sanya kwallo a kan Morelos amma Kelly wanda ke wasa da kyau ya fita daga layin don yin tsayayya.
Amma Livingston ya ci gaba da tilasta wa 'yan wasan waje su yi wasa daidai da yadda suke jin daɗi, tare da Lithgow da Halkett suna shafe dukkan dogon.
Holt ya kamata su fadada su a karshen mataki amma McGregor ya tsaya da kyau don kawar da Jacobs kafin Lithgow ya yi nisa daga kusurwa.
Mai maye gurbin Rangers, Glenn Middleton, ya sake yin fansa lokacin da ya yi jayayya da Jacobs, amma kuma Thomson ya juya fuska.
Almanac: Wanda ya ƙirƙira na'urar lissafin Geiger
Kuma yanzu daga shafin mu na "Sunday Morning" Almanac: Satumba 30, 1882, shekaru 136 da suka wuce a yau, kuma har yanzu za a ci gaba da ƙarawa... ranar da aka haifi masanin kimiyyar lissafi na gaba Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger a Jamus.
Geiger ya kirkiro wata hanya ta gano da kuma auna radiyo, wannan shine abin da ya sa aka kira na'urar Geiger Counter.
A matsayin kayan aikin kimiyya tun daga wannan lokacin, Geiger counter ya zama abin da ya fi dacewa da al'adun gargajiya, kamar a cikin fim din 1950 "Bells of Coronado", wanda ya ƙunshi masanan kimiyya masu ban mamaki Roy Rogers da Dale Evans:
Mutum: Mene ne wannan abu?"
Rogers: "Wannan na'urar lissafin Geiger ce, ana amfani da ita wajen gano ma'adanai masu guba, kamar su uranium.
Sa'ad da ka saka wannan na'urar, za ka iya jin tasirin da atom ke yi a cikin ma'adinai".
Evans: "Ka ce, zai fito yanzu!"
"Hans" Geiger ya mutu a shekara ta 1945, 'yan kwanaki kafin ya cika shekara 63.
Amma abin da ya gano ya sa sunansa ya ci gaba da wanzuwa.
Sabon allurar rigakafin cutar kansa tana koya wa tsarin garkuwar jikinmu gane kwayoyin cutar
Sabon allurar rigakafin cutar kansa tana koya wa jikinmu ya san ƙwayoyin cuta kuma ya kashe su
Rigakafin yana koya wa jikin mutum ya san ƙwayoyin cuta a matsayin wani ɓangare na maganin
Hanyar da yake amfani da ita ita ce, cire ƙwayoyin cuta daga jikin mutum, kuma a yi musu gyara a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje.
Sai suka iya gano sunadaran da suka fi kowa a cikin ciwon daji da yawa, kuma suka sake yin allurar.
Wani rigakafin gwaji ya nuna kyakkyawan sakamako a kan marasa lafiya da ke da ciwon daji iri iri.
Wata mata da aka yi mata maganin rigakafin, wanda ke koya wa tsarin garkuwar jikinta gane ƙwayoyin cuta, ciwon daji na cikin mahaifa ya ɓace mata na tsawon watanni 18.
Wannan hanyar tana ɗauke da ƙwayar jikin mutum da ake kira HER2, wadda ake kira "Heroin", wadda ke da muhimmanci a yawancin ciwon daji.
Farfesa Jay Berzofsky, na Cibiyar Ciwon Ciwon Cutar Amirka a Bethesda, Maryland, ya ce: "Sakamakon ya nuna cewa muna da riga-kafi mai ban al'ajabi".
HER2 tana "inganta ciwon daji da yawa", har da na nono, na ovarian, na huhu, da kuma na colorectal, in ji Farfesa Berzofsky.
Irin wannan tsarin da ake amfani da shi wajen ɗaukan ƙwayoyin cuta na marasa lafiya da kuma koya musu yadda za su kai wa ƙwayoyin daji hari ya yi nasara wajen magance wani ciwon daji.
Kanye West ya fara wani taron nuna goyon bayan Trump, yana saka hat na MAGA, bayan fitowar sa a SNL.
Ba Ya Yi Kyau
An yi wa Kanye West ba'a a cikin studio a lokacin Washegari Night Live bayan wani mummunan wasan kwaikwayon da ya yi inda ya yaba wa Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump kuma ya ce zai tsaya takara a 2020.
Bayan ta yi waka ta uku a daren, mai suna "Ghost Town" inda ta saka hular Make America Great, ta kalubalanci jam'iyyar Democrat kuma ta sake jaddada goyon bayanta ga Trump.
"Na sha yin magana da fararen fata kuma sun ce, "Ta yaya za ku so Trump, shi dan wariyar launin fata ne?"
To, idan na damu da wariyar launin fata, na riga na bar Amurka tun da daɗewa", in ji shi.
SNL ta fara wasan kwaikwayon ne da wani wasan kwaikwayo wanda Matt Damon ya buga inda tauraron Hollywood din ya yi wa Brett Kavanaugh ba'a a shaidar da ya gabatar a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa game da zargin cin zarafin mata da Christine Blasey Ford ta yi.
Ko da yake ba a watsa shi ba, an buga bidiyon magungunan West a kafofin sada zumunta ta hanyar Chris Rock.
Ba a bayyana ko Rock yana son ya yi wa West ba'a da wannan aika-aika ba.
Bugu da ƙari, West ya yi gunaguni ga masu sauraro cewa yana da matsala a bayan fage saboda hat ɗin da aka saka.
"Suna ta yi mini ba'a a bayan fage.
Suka ce, 'Kada ka fita da wannan hat.'
Sun yi mini fashi!
Sai suka ce ina nitsewa", in ji shi, a cewar Washington Examiner.
West ya ci gaba: "Kuna son ganin inda ya nutse?" ya ce zai sa rigar Superman, domin wannan yana nufin ba za ku iya gaya mini abin da zan yi ba.
Ka yi ƙoƙari ka ƙaunace shi".
Maganar ta haifar da ba'a a kalla sau biyu daga masu sauraro kuma SNL ta yi kama da kunya, Variety ta ruwaito, tare da wani ya gaya: "Dukkanin studio ya yi shiru".
An kawo West a lokacin karshe a matsayin mai maye gurbin Ariana Grande, tsohuwar budurwar dan wasan rap din Mac Miller wanda ya mutu kwanakin baya.
West ya rikitar da mutane da yawa tare da yin wasan kwaikwayon "I Love it", yana ado kamar Perrier Bottle.
West ta samu goyon baya daga shugaban kungiyar TPUSA mai ra'ayin mazan jiya, Candace Turner, wadda ta wallafa a shafin Twitter: "Ga daya daga cikin rayuka masu karfin zuciya: Godiya ga ƙaunar da aka yi wa mutane".
Amma mai gabatar da shirin Karen Hunter ta wallafa a shafin Twitter cewa West "yana zama ne kawai kuma yana da kyau kwarai da gaske".
"Amma na zabi BA zan ba da kyauta ga wani (ta hanyar sayen kiɗa ko tufafinsa ko tallafawa "fasaha" na) wanda na yi imanin yana karɓar kuma yana watsa ra'ayoyin da ke da haɗari ga al'ummarmu.
Ya kasance a kan hanya.
Mu ma haka", in ji shi.
Kafin wasan kwaikwayon, mawaƙin ya sanar a shafin Twitter cewa ya canza sunansa, yana mai cewa yanzu shi "mai zama wanda aka sani da Kanye West".
Ba shi ne dan wasan farko da ya canza sunansa ba kuma ya bi diddy, wanda aka fi sani da Puff Daddy, Puffy da P Diddy.
Abokin aikin rap din Snoop Dogg ya sami sunan Snoop Lion kuma tabbas ya mutu Prince, ya canza sunansa zuwa alama kuma daga baya ya zama mai zane-zane wanda aka fi sani da Prince.
