Tauraruwar Game of Thrones Kit Harington ta soki abin da ake kira "masculinity"
Kit Harington ya shahara da yin amfani da takobi a matsayin Jon Snow a cikin wasan kwaikwayo na HBO Game of Thrones.
Amma wannan ɗan wasan, mai shekara 31, ya ƙaryata game da ra'ayin jaruman macho, yana cewa irin wannan rawar a kan allo tana sa samari matasa maza su ji cewa dole ne su kasance masu ƙarfi don a girmama su.
Da yake magana da The Sunday Times Culture, Kit ta ce ta yi imanin 'wani abu ba daidai ba ne' kuma ta yi tambaya game da yadda za a magance matsalar rashin namiji a zamanin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda ya yi aure kwanan nan a wasan kwaikwayon na Game of Thrones Rose Leslie, kuma 31, ya ce yana jin 'da karfi' a kan batun.
'Ina jin kaina, da karfi, a yanzu - ina laifinmu a wannan batun na maza?' in ji shi.
'Menene muka koya wa maza sa'ad da suka girma, game da matsalolin da muke fuskanta a yau?'
Kit ya yi imanin cewa talabijin na iya zama da alhakin bayyanar da mummunan mazauni tare da halayen da suka fi na maza.
Ya ci gaba: 'Wane hali ne aka haifa kuma menene aka koya masa?
Menene ake koyarwa a talabijin, da kuma a kan titi, da ke sa yara maza su ji cewa dole ne su kasance da wannan bangare na musamman na kasancewa namiji?
Ina tsammanin wannan shine ainihin babbar tambaya a zamaninmu - ta yaya zamu canza shi?
Domin akwai wani abu da ba daidai ba game da matasa.'
A cikin wannan hirar ta kuma yarda cewa ba za ta yi wasa a cikin wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones ba lokacin da wasan ya ƙare a lokacin bazara, yana cewa ta 'ƙare da filin yaƙi da dawakai'.
Tun daga watan Nuwamba Kit zai yi fim a True West ta Sam Shepard, wanda ke da labarin wani mai shirya fim da kuma dan uwansa, wanda ya kasance mai fashi.
