HIV/Aids: China ta ba da rahoton ƙaruwar sabbin cututtuka da kashi 14 cikin 100
Kasar Sin ta sanar da cewa yawan mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da kuma cutar kanjamau ya karu da kashi 14 cikin dari.
Fiye da mutane 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar a kasar, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya.
An samu sabbin mutane 40,000 a kwata na biyu na shekarar 2018 kadai.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka suna yaduwa ta hanyar jima'i, suna nuna canji daga baya.
A al'ada, cutar HIV tana yaduwa cikin sauri ta wasu sassan kasar Sin sakamakon kamuwa da jini.
Amma, adadin mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan babu, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin a wani taron da aka yi a lardin Yunnan.
Amma duk da haka, shekara shekara adadin mutanen da suke da HIV da AIDS a China yana ƙaruwa zuwa mutane 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An yi wa luwadi yancin yin jima'i a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma ana zargin cewa nuna bambanci ga mutanen LGBT na karuwa.
Domin ra'ayoyin da suka dace da al'adun ƙasar, bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70-90 na maza da suke yin jima'i da maza za su auri mata.
Yawancin cututtuka da ake samu daga jima'i sun samo asali ne daga rashin kāriya a wannan hanyar.
Tun 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samun damar maganin cutar HIV a ko'ina a kasar, a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance matsalar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa ma'aikatan sun leaked GOP sanata bayanai, yada 'm karya' da kuma 'tsarin hada-hada'
Wakilin majalisar wakilai Maxine Waters a ranar Asabar ta musanta cewa wani ma'aikacinta ya tura bayanan sirri na wasu 'yan majalisar wakilai uku na jam'iyyar Republican zuwa shafin Wikipedia na 'yan majalisar.
'Yan Democrat na Los Angeles sun tabbatar da cewa masana da kuma shafukan yanar gizo na "mai tsattsauran ra'ayi" ne suka yi amfani da wannan da'awar.
"Ƙarya, ƙarya, da sauran ƙaryatãwa", in ji Waters a cikin wata sanarwa a shafin Twitter.
Rahotanni sun ce bayanan da aka fitar sun hada da adireshin gida da kuma lambobin waya na Sanata Lindsey Graham na jihar South Carolina, da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, dukansu 'yan Utah.
Bayanan sun bayyana a Intanet a ranar Alhamis, wanda wani ba a san shi ba ya aika a kan Capitol Hill yayin da ake sauraron kotun majalisar dattawa game da zargin cin zarafin dan takarar babban alkalin kotun Brett Kavanaugh.
Wannan labarin ya fito ne jim kadan bayan da wasu 'yan majalisar dattijai uku suka tambayi Kavanaugh.
Shafukan yanar gizo masu ra'ayin mazan jiya kamar su Gateway Pundit da RedState sun ruwaito cewa adireshin IP da ke gano asalin aika-aikar ya danganta da ofishin Waters kuma ya fallasa bayanin da wani ma'aikacin Waters, Hill ya ruwaito.
"Wannan zargi da ba shi da tushe ba, ba gaskiya ba ne kuma ƙarya ce ta gaske", in ji Waters.
"Mambobin ma'aikatana - waɗanda aka yi wa barazana a kan sunansu, da kuma lafiyarsu ta wajen zargin ƙarya da yaudara - ba su da alhakin wannan ɓarnar.
Wannan zargi da ba shi da tushe ba ƙarya ce kuma ta zama karya".
Sanarwar Waters ta jawo suka kan layi, ciki har da na tsohon sakataren yada labarai na fadar White House Ari Fleischer.
"Wannan hamayya tana nufin fushi", in ji Fleischer.
"Wannan ya nuna cewa bai dace da zama dan majalisa ba.
Idan aka zargi mutum da abin da bai yi ba, ba za su yi fushi ba.
Ba za su iya kaucewa ba.
Ba za su iya tambayar dalilin da ya sa ake tuhumar ba.
Za su kasance da kwanciyar hankali da kuma salama".
Fleischer ya bayyana don kwatanta yadda Waters ya amsa da sukar Democrat game da Alkalin Kavanaugh, wanda masu sukar suka zargi da yin fushi sosai a lokacin shari'ar ranar Alhamis.
Omar Navarro, dan takarar jam'iyyar Republican da ke kokarin kayar da Waters a zaben fidda gwani, shi ma ya bayyana ra'ayinsa a shafin Twitter.
"Babban idan gaskiya ne", ya rubuta a shafinsa na Twitter.
A cikin sanarwar ta, Water ta ce ofishinta ya gargadi "ikon hukuma da hukumomin tilasta yin aiki game da wannan zargi na karya.
"Za mu tabbatar da cewa masu laifin za su bayyana", ya ci gaba, "kuma za su ɗauki alhakin shari'a don duk ayyukan da suka yi da suka lalata da kuma cutar da kowane ɗayan ma'aikatanmu".
