Gaskiya, ya dogara ne da matafiya da kuma wani mutum mai ban mamaki na duniya wanda Atkinson ya buga a cikin tallan TV na Barclaycard wanda yanzu an manta da shi, yana barin rikici a bayansa.
Akwai wani abu mai kyau da ya faru a wannan tafiya ta JE.
Ina son lokacin da Johnny English ya zo wurin jirgin sama a cikin rigar yaƙi na zamanin da kuma sa'ad da turbin ya yi saurin ratayewa a kan kwalkwali.
An nuna kyautar Atkinson don wasan kwaikwayo na jiki, amma abin dariya ya ji daɗi sosai kuma ya yi ban mamaki, musamman lokacin da alamun fina-finai "mai tsanani" kamar 007 da Mission Impossible sun amince da su don haɗa wasan kwaikwayo a matsayin kayan aiki.
Abin dariya ya ji kamar an yi shi ne ga yara maimakon manya, kuma a wurina irin wannan rashin daidaiton Johnny English ba shi da kyau kuma ya mai da hankali kan wasan kwaikwayo na fim din Atkinson a cikin mutum na Bean.
Wani abu da ya yi zafi a cikin shekarun nan shi ne cewa Ingila tana cikin matsala mai tsanani.
Wani dan gwanin kwamfuta ya shiga cikin wani shafin yanar gizo na leken asiri na Birtaniya, ya fallasa duk wani jami'in Birtaniya da ke wurin, don ya bata wa jami'in da ke aiki - abin takaici, Kevin Eldon ya taka rawar gani.
Wannan shi ne na karshe ga firaministan da ake zargi da kuma ƙiyayya, wanda ya rushe cikakken shahararsa a siyasa: Emma Thompson ya yi kyau sosai a matsayin mai kama da Teresa-May amma ba a iya yin abubuwa da yawa daga rubutun ba.
Mai ba shi shawara mai basira ya gaya masa cewa tun da yake an raunana kowane ɗan leƙen asiri da ke aiki, dole ne ya kawo wani daga cikin masu ritaya.
Kuma hakan na nufin cewa Johnny English, wanda shi kansa ɗan iska ne, yanzu yana aiki a matsayin darektan wasu manyan gine-gine, amma yana ba da darasi na sirri game da yadda ake yin aikin ɓoye: akwai wasu kyawawan ban dariya a nan, lokacin da Turanci ya ba da makarantar leken asiri kamar School of Rock.
An dawo da Ingilishi zuwa Whitehall don sanarwar gaggawa kuma an sake haɗuwa da tsohon abokinsa Bough, wanda Ben Miller ya buga.
Bough yanzu ya yi aure, matar wani kwamandan jirgin ruwa, rawar da take takawa a matsayin mace mai ban sha'awa inda Vicki Pepperdine ta kasance mai ban sha'awa.
Sai Batman da Robin suka koma, suka yi wa Mai Girma laifi, suka sadu da kyakkyawar mace mai suna Ophelia Bulletova, wanda Olga Kurylenko ta buga.
A halin yanzu, firaministan ya fada cikin halin damuwa na wani attajiri mai fasaha wanda ya yi ikirarin cewa zai iya warware matsalar kwamfutar Ingila: Jason Volta, wanda Jake Lacy ya buga.
English da Bough sun fara kasada: suna ɓoye a matsayin masu hidima, sun ƙona gidan cin abinci na Faransa; sun yi rikici ta hanyar shiga cikin jirgin ruwan Volta mai tsada; kuma English ya haifar da rashin tsari lokacin da ya yi ƙoƙarin amfani da kayan aikin Virtual Reality don ya san abin da ke cikin gidan Volta.
An cire duk wani abin da ya rage don jerin karshe, amma tare da irin wannan sadaukarwa da kuma rashin jin daɗi, akwai ƙananan tashoshin TV na yara da ke da komai.
Abu ne mai matsakaici.
Kuma kamar sauran fina-finan Johnny English, ba zan iya daina tunani ba: Shin masana'antar fim ta Burtaniya ba za ta iya ba Rowan Atkinson rawar da ta dace da baiwa ba?
Ma'aikata na zanga-zanga suna tsara shirin cewa 'yan Birtaniya za su yi aiki kwana hudu a mako amma a biya su kwana biyar.
Jeremy Corbyn na jam'iyyar Labour ya yi la'akari da wani tsari mai tsauri da zai bukaci 'yan Birtaniya su yi aiki kwana hudu a mako - amma a biya su kwana biyar.
An ruwaito cewa kungiyar tana son masu kamfanoni su ci gaba da samun kudin shiga ta hanyar juyin juya halin kere kere (AI) ga ma'aikata ta hanyar basu karin ranakun hutu.
Zai bar ma'aikatansa su yi hutu na kwana uku - amma a biya su daidai.
Wasu majiyoyi sun ce wannan ra'ayin zai 'dace' da tsarin tattalin arzikin jam'iyyar da kuma shirin da ke karfafawa jihar gwiwa wajen tallafawa ma'aikata.
An amince da sauyawar zuwa kwanaki hudu a mako ta hanyar majalisar kasuwanci ta Burtaniya a matsayin hanyar da za ta bai wa ma'aikata damar jin dadin amfanin canjin tattalin arziki.
Wani babban jami'in ƙungiyar ma'aikata ya gaya wa The Sunday Times: 'Ana sa ran za a yi nazari a kan wannan dokar kafin ƙarshen wannan shekara.
'Wannan ba zai faru ba dare ɗaya, amma kwana huɗu na aiki a mako shi ne burin da ya dace da tsarin jam'iyyar don daidaita tattalin arziki wanda ke tallafa wa ma'aikata da kuma dabarun masana'antar jam'iyyar gaba ɗaya.'
Jam'iyyar Labor ba ita ce ta farko da ta goyi bayan wannan ra'ayin ba, saboda Jam'iyyar Green ta yi alkawarin yin aiki kwana hudu a mako a lokacin yakin neman zaben 2017.
Amma a yanzu, ba a amince da wannan burin ba a duk jam'iyyar.
Wani kakakin jam'iyyar ya ce: 'Aikin kwana huɗu a mako ba manufa ba ce kuma ba a yin la'akari da shi.'
Shadow Chancellor John McDonnell ya yi amfani da taron ma'aikata na makon da ya gabata don kammala hangen nesan sa na juyin juya halin zamantakewar al'umma a fannin tattalin arziki.
McDonnell ya ce yana da niyyar sake karbo iko daga shuwagabannin da ba a san su ba da kuma masu zanen kaya a kamfanonin samar da wutar lantarki.
Wannan shirin na shugaba na inuwa kuma yana nufin cewa, masu hannun jari na yanzu a kamfanin ruwan sha mai yiwuwa ba za su sami duk hannun jarin su ba saboda gwamnatin Labor na iya yin 'yanci' bisa dalilin keta doka.
Ya kuma tabbatar da shirinsa na sanya ma'aikata a kan kwamitin gudanarwa na kamfanin da kuma samar da Asusun Mallaka na Musamman wanda zai ba da kashi 10 cikin 100 na hannun jari na kamfanoni a cikin kamfanoni masu zaman kansu ga ma'aikata, wanda zai ba da ribar shekara-shekara har zuwa £500.
Lindsey Graham, John Kennedy ya gaya wa "60 Minutes" cewa binciken da FBI ke yi game da Kavanaugh zai iya canja ra'ayinsu
Binciken da hukumar ta FBI ke yi game da zargin da ake yi wa mai shari'a Brett Kavanaugh ya dage zaben da za a yi na neman takararsa a kotun koli na kasar nan har tsawon mako guda, kuma hakan ya tayar da tambaya kan ko binciken hukumar zai iya rinjayar 'yan majalisar dattijai daga jam'iyyar Republican su janye goyon bayansu.
A wata hira da aka yi da 'yan jaridar "60 Minutes" Scott Pelley, wanda ya fito a ranar Lahadi, ya tambayi Sanata John Kennedy da Lindsey Graham, 'yan Republican, ko hukumar ta FBI za ta iya gano wani abu da zai sa su canja ra'ayinsu.
Kamar dai Kennedy ya fi abokinsa na South Carolina.
"Ina nufin, ba shakka", in ji Kennedy.
"Na ce zan halarci shari'a, na ce, na yi magana da Alkalin Kavanaugh.
Na kira shi bayan wannan lamarin, zargin ya bayyana, kuma ya ce, 'Shin kun yi hakan?'
"Ya kasance mai tsananin ƙarfi, mai tsananin ƙarfi".
Amma, kamar dai ba za a iya canja muryar Graham ba.
"Tunanina ya riga ya yanke hukunci game da Brett Kavanaugh, kuma yana bukatar karin zargi don canza shi", in ji shi.
"Dr. Ford, ban san abin da ya faru ba, amma abin da na sani shi ne: Brett ya musanta hakan da ƙarfi", Graham ya kara da cewa, yana nufin Christine Blasey Ford.
"Kuma duk wanda ya ambaci sunansa ba zai iya tabbatar da hakan ba.
Yana da shekara 36.
Ban ga wani canji ba".
Menene bikin Global Citizen kuma shin wannan bikin ya yi wani abu ne wajen rage talauci?
A wannan Asabar, New York za ta yi bikin Global Citizen Festival, wani biki na shekara-shekara na kiɗa da ke nuna jerin taurari masu ban mamaki da kuma manufa mai ban mamaki: kawo ƙarshen talauci a duniya.
A yanzu, a shekara ta bakwai, bikin Global Citizen zai ga dubun dubatan mutane suna zuwa babban lawn a Central Park ba wai kawai don jin dadin Janet Jackson, Cardi B, da Shawn Mendes ba, amma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin manufar bikin, wato kawo karshen matsanancin talauci a shekarar 2030.
Bikin Global Citizen, wanda aka fara a shekarar 2012, ci gaba ne na Global Poverty Project, wata kungiya ta kasa da kasa da ke fatan kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke fafutukar yaki da talauci.
Don samun tikiti kyauta don taron (sai dai idan kuna son biyan tikitin VIP), masu halartar za su kammala jerin ayyuka ko ayyuka kamar su ba da gudummawa, aika imel ga shugabannin duniya, yin kira, ko wasu hanyoyi masu ma'ana don taimakawa wajen wayar da kan jama'a game da burin su na kawar da talauci.
Amma, yaya Global Citizen ta yi nasara a cikin shekaru 12 na cimma burinta?
