Masu kirkirar yanar gizo suna shirin fara sabuwar intanet domin su yi gogayya da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, ya kaddamar da wani kamfanin da zai yi gogayya da Facebook, Amazon, da Google.
Sabon aikin wannan almara na fasaha, Inrupt, kamfani ne da aka gina daga Berners-Lee, dandamali mai budewa, Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda aka adana bayanan su da kuma wanda aka ba izinin samun damar kowane irin bayani.
A wata hira ta musamman da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi wa'azin cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce "mulkin duniya".
"Ya kamata mu fara yanzu", in ji ta daga farawa.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi".
Wannan aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid wanda ke bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar "tushen bayanan kan layi na sirri" ko POD nasu.
Wannan ajiyar tana iya ƙunsar jerin lambobin sadarwa, jerin ayyuka, kalandarku, laburarenku na waƙa, da kuma wasu kayan aiki na sana'a da na sirri.
Kamar Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack, da Spotify duk suna cikin burauzar yanar gizo ɗaya kuma duk a lokaci guda.
Abin da ke na musamman game da adana bayanan sirri na kan layi shi ne, yana da cikakken iko akan wanda mai amfani zai iya samun damar irin bayanan da yake da su.
A cikin kamfanoni, ana kiranta "inganta mutum ta hanyar bayanai".
Manufar kafa Inrupt, a cewar Shugaba John Bruce, ita ce kamfanin ya samar da albarkatu, da hanyoyin aiki, da kuma basira da suka dace domin taimakawa wajen samar da Solid ga kowa.
A yau, kamfanin ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu masu haɓaka ma'aikata da aka ba da izini don yin aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shiryen shirye-shirye.
Farawa daga wannan makon, masu fasahar kere kere a duk duniya za su iya gina nasu aikace-aikacen rarraba ta hanyar amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba su yi magana da "Facebook da Google ba game da ko za su gabatar da sauyi na gaba daya inda duk tsarin kasuwancin su za a juya su cikin dare.
"Ba mu nemi izininsu ba".
A cikin wani rubutu a Medium da aka buga a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa "umurnin Inrupt shi ne samar da makamashi da kuma tsarin kasuwanci don taimakawa kare mutunci da ingancin sabon gidan yanar gizo da aka gina akan Solid".
A 1994, Berners-Lee ya canza Intanet lokacin da ya kafa World Wide Web Consortium a Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya zama mai tasiri a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na hanyar sadarwa.
Ko da lokacin da ya kaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai kasance wanda ya kafa kuma ya zama darektan World Wide Web Consortium, Gidauniyar Yanar gizo, da kuma Cibiyar Bayanai ta Bude.
"Ina da kyakkyawan fata game da zamanin yanar gizo na gaba", in ji Berners-Lee.
Bernard Vann: Tunawa da malamai na WW1 Victoria Cross
An tuna da limamin Coci na Ingila wanda ya lashe Victoria Cross a lokacin yakin duniya na farko a matsayin mayaƙi a ƙasar haihuwarsa shekaru 100 bayan haka.
Lt. Col. The Reverend Bernard Vann ya lashe kyautar ne a ranar 29 ga watan Satumba na shekarar 1918 saboda hare-haren da aka kai a Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Amma, kwana huɗu bayan haka, wani ɗan bindiga ya kashe shi ba tare da ya san cewa ya sami babban daraja na soja ba.
'Ya'yansa biyu ne suka yi bikin buɗe wani dutse na tunawa da shi a wani biki a Rushden, Northamptonshire, a ranar Asabar.
Ɗaya daga cikin jikokinsa, Michael Vann, ya ce wannan dutse "alama ce ta basira" wadda za ta bayyana daidai shekaru 100 na nasarar da kakansa ya samu.
A ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, a cewar jaridar London Gazette, Laftanar Kanal Vann ya ja-goranci rundunarsa ta ƙetare Canal de Saint-Quentin "ta hanyar hazo mai yawa da ke ƙarƙashin harbin bindigogi da na'urori".
Sai ya ruga zuwa ga fagen fama kuma da "ƙarfin hali" ya jagoranci gaba kafin ya yi hanzari ya yi amfani da bindiga shi kaɗai kuma ya kashe ƙungiyoyi uku.
An kashe Laftanar Kanar Vann a hannun 'yan bindiga na Jamus a ranar 4 ga Oktoba, 1918 - fiye da wata ɗaya kafin yaƙin ya ƙare.
Michael Vann, mai shekara 72, ya ce abin da kakansa ya yi "wani abu ne da na sani ba zan iya rayuwa ba amma abin da ya yi ya nuna cewa na ƙasƙantar da kaina sosai".
Shi da ɗan'uwansa Dr James Vann sun kuma ajiye furanni bayan bikin, wanda ƙungiyar matasa ta Brentwood ta jagoranci.
Michael Vann ya ce "yana jin daɗin shiga cikin wannan bikin" kuma ya kara da cewa "za a nuna jarumin jarumi na gaskiya tare da goyon bayan da mutane da yawa za su bayar".
MMA masu goyon baya sun tsaya duk dare suna kallon Bellator 206, amma sun sami Peppa Pig
