Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami sun addabi ƙasar Indonesia
Girgizar kasa da tsunami mai karfin gaske da ta afkawa birnin Palu na kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, sun yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane 384, jami'an tsaro sun ce, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Rashin sadarwa ya sa jami'an agaji suka yi ta neman bayanai daga gundumar Donggala, wani yanki da ke arewacin Palu wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasar mai karfin 7.5.
A Palu, bayan bala'in, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu shine babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, wanda ke kan iyakar bakin tekun yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da yawan mutane 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku, birnin yana bikin cika shekara 40 da haihuwa.
Donggala, a halin yanzu, gundumar da ke da nisan kilomita 300 (180 mil) daga gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Gundumar, wacce ke da yanki a karkashin lardin, an kiyasta tana da mutane 299,200 a shekarar 2017.
Babban tattalin arzikin lardin na Sulawesi ta Kudu shine kamun kifi da kuma noman dabbobi, musamman a gabar tekun Donggala.
Duk da haka, kasancewar ma'adinan nickel ma yana taka muhimmiyar rawa a lardin, kodayake galibi yana cikin Morowali, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
A cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da tsunami sau da yawa, bisa ga bayanan Hukumar Kula da Bala'in Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, mutane fiye da 200 suka mutu a wata bala'in tsunami kuma ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala suka lalace.
A shekara ta 1996, mutane tara sun mutu a lokacin da aka yi wata bala'i mai girma a yammacin Donggala.
A fannin girgizar ƙasa, Indonesia tana kan Rukunin Wuta na Fasifik, saboda haka, ana yawan samun girgizar ƙasa.
A cikin 'yan shekarun nan, an yi wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami kamar haka:
2004: A ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, an yi wata babbar girgizar kasa a Indonesia, a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh, a arewacin Sumatra, wanda ya haifar da tsunami a kasashe 14, har ya yi sanadiyyar mutuwar mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, kuma fiye da rabin wadanda suka mutu suna Aceh.
2005: A ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu, girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa gaɓar yammacin Sumatra.
A tsibirin Nias, a gabar Sumatra, an yi mutuwar daruruwan mutane.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 6.8 ta afka kudu da Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta jawo tsunami a gaɓar tekun kudu inda kusan mutane 700 suka mutu.
2009: An yi wata girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.6 a kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin yammacin Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 suka mutu.
2010: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 da ya auku a tsibirin Mentawai da ke Sumatra ya sa tsunami mai tsawon kafa 10 ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Gundumar Pidie Jaya ta Aceh, ta kuma fuskanci girgizar kasa mai zurfi da ta haifar da bala'i, da kuma fargaba daga mutanen da ke tunawa da lalacewar da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka yi a shekarar 2004.
Ko da yake ba a iya samun wata babbar ambaliyar ruwa ba, amma sama da mutane 100 sun mutu a sakamakon rushewar ginin.
