An zargi Saipov, mai shekara 30, da aikata wannan mummunan aiki ta hanyar yin tir da wata babbar mota da ya yi haya daga Home Depot zuwa ga masu tafiya da ƙafa da masu hawan keke a kan hanyar keke a gefen West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, a watan Oktoba.
